          <a href="/" class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] underline decoration-[var(--color-border)] underline-offset-4 transition-colors">&larr; Back to home</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[12px] text-[oklch(60%_0.005_250)] mt-8 font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)]">
          Rules link to <a class="underline decoration-[var(--color-border)] underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-[var(--color-text-secondary)]" href="/docs/ui-craft-detect">ui-craft-detect</a> documentation.
